CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper May 11, 1957, pg. A8, reads: "Young Models - These lovely young ladies modeled toddler fashions for springtime at the annual Fashion Fantasy, Sunday, at the Anna B. Heldman Center, sponsored by the Pittsburgh Scholarship Guild. They are, left to right, first row: Michele Jones, Paulette Young and Darlene Robinson. Second row: 'Bunnie' Kemp, Jacqueline Washington, Toni Jones, Kitty Johnson, Kathy More, Barbara Washington and Carolyn Paxton. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Models in "Fashion Fantasy" show, seated from left: Michele Jones, Paulette Young, Darlene Robinson; standing: 'Bunnie' Kemp, Jacqueline Washington, Toni Jones, Kitty Johnson, Kathy More, Barbara Washington and Carolyn Paxton posed in Anna B. Heldman Center
